prayer before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the caller to prayer announced the prayer, people among the companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would stand and proceed to the pillars of the mosque until the Prophet came out to them. Thus, they would pray two cycles before sunset\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36424,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-between-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36424,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Continuous praying between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I performed the evening prayer with him. The Prophet continued to pray until the evening prayer. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3781 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/12-rakaat-al-sunan-al-rawatib\/","url_meta":{"origin":36424,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Twelve raka\u2019at of al-Sunan al-Rawatib prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perseveres in performing twelve cycles of prayer from the Sunnah, Allah will build a house for him in Paradise. They are four cycles before noon prayer and two after it, two cycles after sunset prayer, two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33619,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/sunan-maghrib-if-you-wish\/","url_meta":{"origin":36424,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recommended two raka&#8217;at before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Muzanni reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPray before the sunset prayer.\u201d The Prophet said on the third time, \u201cFor whomever wishes,\u201d as he disliked for people to consider it an obligatory tradition. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1183 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36424","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=36424"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36424\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=36424"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=36424"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":tru